      "acceptanceCriteria": "Ansys Mechanical commercial FEA code used under documented QA procedures; version control and validation suite records available.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical is a commercially released, widely validated FEA solver. The modeling team maintains version-controlled input decks and follows an internal SQA plan aligned with ASME V&V 10 guidance. Required level 2 achieved."
